Job Description:
As a Commercial Assistant of the USV Service Line you will support the business with ongoing commercial activities, like: organizing tender packages, updating our ERP system, liasing with other Fugro departments. USVs are one of Fugro’s key focus areas to enabling delivery of our projects in a safer and more sustainable way. You will be part of a new regional team, responsible for its successful implementation. In this role you support the commercial manager and the proposal managers with responding to commercial opportunities with new and existing clients
Your role
You support commercial managers in preparing tenders and pre-qualification questionnaires;
You assist proposal leads with creation, compilation, and QA/QC of commercial documents;
